# Symlink to a local grid-editor checkout, created by scripts/link-grid-editor.sh
# (npm run gen-docs:local / build:local) to reproduce the reference manual pipeline locally.
/grid-editor

# Reference manual pages regenerated from grid-editor's LuaCATS annotations on every build
# (see scripts/postprocess-generated-docs.mjs and the .github/actions/generate-api-docs
# step used by the firebase-hosting-*/generate-api-docs workflows) - not hand-authored, so
# not tracked. Listed explicitly rather than ignoring the whole reference-manual/ tree,
# since introduction.md and grid-functions/index.md in the same directories *are*
# hand-authored and must stay tracked.
/docs/reference-manual/control-element-functions/_category_.json
/docs/reference-manual/control-element-functions/element.md
/docs/reference-manual/control-element-functions/button.md
/docs/reference-manual/control-element-functions/encoder.md
